00:27:22.000 --> 00:27:29.000
And that will make sure that as I'm making these changes to these files, they behave the way we expect.

00:27:30.000 --> 00:27:37.000
The other thing I'll do, since this isn't on, is I'll just turn this option on so we strip additional space at the end of lines.

